  "lastUpdatedOn": "2013-03-26",
  "religion": "Val Kilmer is a devout Christian Scientist.",
  "politicalViews": "He is a liberal Democrat, and sometimes even farther to the left than that.",
  "author": "Caitlin Frye",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 1
    },
    {
      "parentId": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Val Kilmer was born and raised in Los Angeles, California."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 2
    },
    {
      "parentId": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Kilmer grew up as, and is currently a Christian Scientist. Or, to clarify, as he said in an interview in 2005,"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 3
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 4,
      "parentId": 3
    },
    {
      "parentId": 4,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Well, I am trying to be. It is quite a challenging faith.",
      "sourceTitle": "Crazy Things Seem Normal . . . Normal Things Seem Crazy.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.esquire.com/features/ESQ0705VALKILMER_120"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 5
    },
    {
      "parentId": 5,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Despite that statement, Kilmer is clearly very devoted spiritually. He said,"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 6
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 7,
      "parentId": 6
    },
    {
      "parentId": 7,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "I am a religious person. I do pray for specific needs. I do read the Bible every Sunday. I've read the Bible all of my life. I also pray for things that are going on in the world; it has given me a deeper sense of responsibility as a person.",
      "sourceTitle": "Val Kilmer shows his spiritual side as he visits the Wailing Wall in Jerusalem.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1217585/Val-Kilmer-shows-spiritual-visits-Wailing-Wall-Jerusalem.html"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 8
    },
    {
      "parentId": 8,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "He also wrote, directed, and starred in a play about the relationship between the founder of Christian Science, Mary Baker Eddy, and Mark Twain.",
      "sourceTitle": "Val Kilmer's One Man Show: 'Citizen Twain' To Run At The Hollywood Forever Cemetery, Kilmer Hopes To 'Be Redeemed.'",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/03/26/val-kilmers-one-man-show_n_1381279.html"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 8,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " He made a pilgrimage to the Western Wall in Jerusalem.",
      "sourceTitle": "Val Kilmer shows his spiritual side as he visits the Wailing Wall in Jerusalem.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1217585/Val-Kilmer-shows-spiritual-visits-Wailing-Wall-Jerusalem.html"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 8,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " And to top it all off, here was the actor's Twitter message over Christmas in 2012 from the song \"Little Town of Bethlehem:\""
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 9
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 10,
      "parentId": 9
    },
    {
      "parentId": 10,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "How silently, how silently/ The wondrous gift is given!/ So God imparts to human hearts/ The blessings of His heaven.",
      "sourceTitle": "ValEKilmer: How silently, how silently The …",
      "sourceUrl": "https://twitter.com/ValEKilmer/status/283611989987692544"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 11
    },
    {
      "parentId": 11,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "And there you have it.\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "id": 12
    },
    {
      "parentId": 12,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Just looking for ways to contribute"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 13
    },
    {
      "parentId": 13,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Kilmer's politics are definitely left-leaning, and he's a registered Democrat,",
      "sourceTitle": "Val Kilmer ponders running for governor.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.nbcnews.com/id/29048706/#.UUzYvxyG2wc"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 13,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " but he seems to lean a little left of the mainstream party. He voted for Obama, at least in 2008,",
      "sourceTitle": "Val Kilmer ponders running for governor.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.nbcnews.com/id/29048706/#.UUzYvxyG2wc"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 13,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " but the majority of his campaign contributions went to the more liberal independent candidate Ralph Nader that year.",
      "sourceTitle": "Donor Lookup: Find Individual and Soft Money Contributors.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.opensecrets.org/indivs/search.php?name=kilmer%2C+val&state=&zip=&employ=&cand=&c2012=Y&c2010=Y&c2008=Y&sort=N&capcode=bptxq&submit=Submit+your+Donor+Query"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 14
    },
    {
      "parentId": 14,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Although he doesn't get himself too entrenched in the latest Hollywood liberal causes, Kilmer does appear to be concerned with environmental issues.",
      "sourceTitle": "Val Kilmer slashes the asking price of his eco-ranch.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://planetforward.ca/blog/val-kilmer-slashes-the-asking-price-on-his-eco-ranch/"
    },
    {
      "parentId": 14,
      "type": "text",
      "text": " And he considered running for governor of New Mexico at one point because, as he said,"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "id": 15
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 16,
      "parentId": 15
    },
    {
      "parentId": 16,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "I'm just looking for ways to be contributive. And if that ends up being where I can make a substantial contribution, then I'll run.",
      "sourceTitle": "Val Kilmer ponders running for governor.",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.nbcnews.com/id/29048706/#.UUzYvxyG2wc"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": 17
    },
    {
      "parentId": 17,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Well, that hasn't happened yet, but keep us informed, Hollowverse readers. We could have another Hollywood politician on our hands."
    }
  ],
